longBusinessSummary: Natural Capsules Limited engages in manufacture and sale of hard gelatin and cellulose capsule shells in India and internationally. The company offers bovine spongiform encephalopathy and transmissible spongiform encephalopathy free gelatin, shiny gelatin, sodium lauryl sulfate free gelatin, halal certified gelatin, fast release gelatin, printed gelatin/cellulose, vegetarian, and enteric capsule shells. It is also involved in formulating pharmaceutical dosage forms in capsule dosage form. The company also exports its products. Natural Capsules Limited was incorporated in 1993 and is based in Bengaluru, India.
